➜天际汽车的首款量产车体验营开启！天际ME7体验营上海站圆满收官
http://www.sohu.com/a/437468906_99994080	38071
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201210/207d81e143624387a725ae351e914284.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
