➜对标蔚来！定位更高，长城或将推出全新高端新能源品牌
http://www.sohu.com/a/437490205_99994080	47413
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201210/f9128830737d4951a6d5ab6680b43309.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201210/419f19a817a0467c9a50b2d9b6e394c3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201210/ca895d4514a04691a405ea1c201e7d41.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
